name: ChoreWars
0:
”Alexa, open chore wars”
”Alexa, set up chore wars”
”Alexa, check chore wars”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chore wars
des: This skill will report this week's running XP totals for your party similar to the totals on the "This Week" page on the website. This Alexa skill will read from your party's chorewars.com RSS feed. The RSS feed won't list the chores of an adventurer who has their privacy set to "just my party".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
